                            <h3 class="title">Network Management</h3>
                            <p class="mb-30">At BMS Infosolution Software Technology, we offer comprehensive Provider Network Management services that enable healthcare payers to build, manage, and optimize strong provider networks. Our solutions ensure smooth collaboration between payers and healthcare providers, improving member access to quality care while maintaining compliance with regulatory standards and contractual obligations.</p>

                            <p class="mb-30">Our services cover the entire provider lifecycle—from credentialing and onboarding to contract management and performance analytics. We streamline provider data validation, reduce administrative delays, and ensure that network directories are up-to-date and accurate. With our robust technology and expert team, healthcare payers can minimize provider friction, improve transparency, and ensure better care coordination for members.</p>

                            <p class="mb-30">By choosing BMS Infosolution, payers gain a strategic partner in managing provider relationships, ensuring network adequacy, and supporting value-based care initiatives. Our flexible, tech-enabled platform enhances network visibility, tracks provider performance, and supports real-time updates for efficient communication and service delivery.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><img src="assets/images/icon/arrow-icon-3.png" alt="">End-to-End Provider Lifecycle Management – Credentialing, contracting, onboarding, and updates in one place.</li>
