                                <li><img src="assets/images/icon/arrow-icon-3.png" alt="">Compliance & Regulatory Readiness – Ensure alignment with CMS, NCQA, and state-specific requirements.</li>
                                <li><img src="assets/images/icon/arrow-icon-3.png" alt="">Provider Performance Monitoring – Track KPIs like quality scores, utilization, and contract adherence.</li>
                                <li><img src="assets/images/icon/arrow-icon-3.png" alt="">Interoperable & Scalable Platform – Seamless integration with existing payer systems and EHRs.</li>
